                            Line 1: "M&A Advisory" → <span class="code-vignette-info">GL 6-2000 (Consulting)</span><br>
                            Line 2: "Filing Fees" → <span class="code-vignette-info">GL 4-1000 (Govt Fees)</span><br>
                            Line 3: "Disbursements" → <span class="code-vignette-info">GL 2-5000 (Billable)</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="time-savings">Result: Removes 90% of manual coding decisions.</p>
                    </div>
